---
layout: base.njk
title: Newsletter
description: Long-form philosophical writing from the Axiom Society, NSUT.
---

<div class="main">
  <div class="page-header">
    <p class="eyebrow">Axiom Writes</p>
    <h1>The Newsletter</h1>
    <p>Essays, reflections, and philosophical musings — written by us, for everyone who thinks.</p>
  </div>

  <div style="text-align:center; margin-bottom: 2.5rem; display:flex; justify-content:center;">
    <div style="display:flex; align-items:center; gap:0.6rem; font-family:var(--font-mono); font-size:0.65rem; letter-spacing:0.15em; text-transform:uppercase; color:rgba(26,26,24,0.45);">
      <svg width="13" height="13" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24" style="color:var(--color-gold); flex-shrink:0;">
        <path d="M6.18 15.64a2.18 2.18 0 010 4.36 2.18 2.18 0 010-4.36M4 4.44A15.56 15.56 0 0119.56 20h-2.83A12.73 12.73 0 006.18 7.27V4.44M4 10.1a9.9 9.9 0 019.9 9.9H11.1A7.07 7.07 0 004 12.93V10.1z"/>
      </svg>
      Follow in your reader —
      <a href="/newsletter/feed.xml" style="color:var(--color-terracotta); text-decoration:none;">RSS</a>
      <span style="color:rgba(26,26,24,0.2);">⋅</span>
      <a href="/newsletter/atom.xml" style="color:var(--color-terracotta); text-decoration:none;">Atom</a>
    </div>
  </div>

  {% if collections.posts.length %}
    <div class="post-list">
      {% for post in collections.posts %}
        <article class="post-item">
          <p class="post-date">
            <time datetime="{{ post.date | isoDate }}">{{ post.date | readableDate }}</time>
          </p>
          <h2 class="post-title">
            <a href="{{ post.url | withPrefix }}">{{ post.data.title }}</a>
          </h2>
          {% if post.data.author %}
            <p class="post-author">by {{ post.data.author }}</p>
          {% endif %}
          {% if post.data.excerpt %}
            <p class="post-excerpt">{{ post.data.excerpt }}</p>
          {% endif %}
          <a href="{{ post.url | withPrefix }}" class="post-read-more">Read essay →</a>
        </article>
      {% endfor %}
    </div>
  {% else %}
    <p style="color: rgba(26,26,24,0.5); text-align:center; padding: 4rem 0;">
      The first issue is being written. Check back soon.
    </p>
  {% endif %}
</div>
